22
00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:54.388
[Robinshaw] I'm sorry.
I don't speak Spanish.

23
00:00:54.522 --> 00:00:55.823
Pull up Martian's phone

24
00:00:55.889 --> 00:00:57.891
