and our weapons systems.

43
00:02:21.141 --> 00:02:22.142
♪ Tense music ♪

44
00:02:22.243 --> 00:02:24.478
So you need us.

45
00:02:24.612 --> 00:02:26.380
Do we need you?

46
00:02:26.480 --> 00:02:28.282
We are aware that
you're currently negotiating

47
00:02:28.382 --> 00:02:29.650
